Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.75,0:06:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 我怀孕了  - 什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.04,0:06:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}不会吧！你怀孕了？卡拉你怎么不早说？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.17,0:06:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我事情比较多 总有个丢三落四的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.39,0:06:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}职业妇女嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.06,0:06:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}恭喜你 还怕你不想再生了
