Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.19,0:07:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}要不是它有悖于我最珍贵的信仰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.69,0:07:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}"男人都是臭混蛋"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.78,0:07:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}到底是谁啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.45,0:07:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}马修！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.37,0:07:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 马修？ - 卡拉和"麻理工"的"打狗脱"好上了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.58,0:07:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}如果你们不好意思当着我明说 那就别说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.84,0:07:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}不是 教练
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.55,0:07:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}马修就是卡拉肚里孩子的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.55,0:07:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}马修？真不敢相信 我可什么都信的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.85,0:07:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 你身子还好吗？孩儿他妈？ - 跟你定个协议
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.23,0:07:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}你不叫我"孩儿他妈"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.19,0:08:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我就不把你的舌头放进果汁机里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.69,0:08:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 马修 快过来坐下  - 快请坐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.74,0:08:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 好样的  - 真为你俩高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.37,0:08:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 祝贺你！ - 祝贺你 要当爸爸了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.66,0:08:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}你也快坐下 孩儿他... 卡拉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.75,0:08:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.88,0:08:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}必须庆祝一下 来点香槟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.00,0:08:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 祝酒！ - 给我端上来！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.34,0:08:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我来摆杯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.88,0:08:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}顺便说一句 向你推荐"呼吸分娩法"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.30,0:08:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我在书里读到过 相当管用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.93,0:08:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}用不着 我有独门秘技
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.22,0:08:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}一拳揍昏我 等教小孩拉尿时再把我叫醒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.82,0:08:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我们祝酒吧 谁来致祝酒词
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.49,0:08:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 黛安 你来祝酒  - 好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.16,0:08:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}祝新生儿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.87,0:08:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}有马修这位父亲 必然头脑聪慧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.33,0:08:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}有卡拉这位母亲 更需要补充头脑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.50,0:09:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}开玩笑的 我的意思是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.92,0:09:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}为新生儿 和他有幸拥有如此优秀的父母而干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.34,0:09:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}干杯！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.18,0:09:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.43,0:09:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我想去稍微躺会儿 行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.31,0:09:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}失陪 我待会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.18,0:09:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我一点不知道你和卡拉在交往
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.10,0:09:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}实际上我们只约会过一次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.57,0:09:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}一次？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.53,0:09:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}只约过一次？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.20,0:09:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我也很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.91,0:09:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}因为卡拉之前从不多看我一眼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.04,0:09:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}之后也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.50,0:09:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}但那一晚她完全对我投怀送抱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.88,0:09:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}简直热情如火
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.84,0:09:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}所以整件事都是她的主意？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.80,0:09:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}是的 可以这样讲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.97,0:09:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我并非不享受
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.22,0:09:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}但我完全没料到事情的发展
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.93,0:10:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}她昨天告诉我的时候 我真是大吃一惊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.94,0:10:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}不好意思 我要去和卡拉谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.95,0:10:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 你真是太聪明啦  - 啥意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.45,0:10:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我知道你打的什么主意 你这个滑头
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.41,0:10:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我甘拜下风 太高明了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.21,0:10:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 不知道你在说啥  - 你知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.75,0:10:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}马修不是你肚里孩子的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.55,0:10:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}他也许是 也许不是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.39,0:10:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}拜托 卡拉 你可以告诉我实话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.02,0:10:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我很为你骄傲 女人就应该占据主动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.44,0:10:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}好吧 既然你已经猜到了\N你说得对 他不是孩子的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.40,0:10:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我骗他当便宜老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.28,0:10:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}真是一条妙计
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.78,0:10:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我得意地想给自己哼个小曲儿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.29,0:11:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}不用哼小曲儿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.50,0:11:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}给我像这样使劲哼哼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.17,0:11:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}卡拉 你怎么能这样做呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.80,0:11:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}你何不坐下 让我给你好好说说？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.72,0:11:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.18,0:11:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}那天我过得特别衰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.23,0:11:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}被客人逃了两次小费
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.31,0:11:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}山姆莫名其妙大骂我一顿 你又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.02,0:11:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}回家路上被淋了个落汤鸡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.57,0:11:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}回家发现我把小孩锁在了他们的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.45,0:11:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我实在受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.87,0:11:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}所以我坐在厨房桌子上 拿着一瓶红酒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.00,0:11:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}开始思考我的人生怎会这么倒霉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.30,0:11:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}就在那时 我从落地窗外的雾气中看到了他的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.35,0:12:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 谁啊？ - 尼克 我的前夫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.39,0:12:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}再加上那天还是我们的结婚纪念日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.98,0:12:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.57,0:12:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}只怪我当时太消沉 我本来只想和他聊两句
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.36,0:12:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}所以我们喝了点酒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.57,0:12:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}回忆我俩以前屈指可数的几天快活日子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.87,0:12:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}那是我全天第一次有笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.33,0:12:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}他穿着他的黑色渔网式汗衫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.71,0:12:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}从洞洞里可以看到他的豹子纹身
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.80,0:12:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}没有女人能够抗拒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.85,0:12:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}外面风大雨大 酒精又催劲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.77,0:12:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}姐就冲动了一把
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.19,0:12:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}卡拉 这个男人就是你说过的那个"漏屎专家"吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.20,0:13:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}没错 尼克是特别恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.58,0:13:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}但他知道我耳垂上的死穴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}咬一口就能让我变成一滩烂泥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.46,0:13:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我可一点也不信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.54,0:13:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 不信？  - 不信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.17,0:13:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 那我做给你看  - 卡拉 你别闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.93,0:13:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}卡拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.64,0:13:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}克里夫 我们不是你想的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.64,0:13:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}没关系 我是八十年代新一辈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.52,0:13:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 先锋电影看得多了  - 不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.03,0:13:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}克里夫 你要明白 卡拉和我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.24,0:13:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}正在测试一项特别吸引人的科学假说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.37,0:13:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}科学！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.20,0:13:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我喜欢科学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.58,0:13:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}请这边来 卡拉 试给他看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.38,0:13:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 想不到吧  - 我啥感觉也没有
