Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.63,0:18:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 我回家了  - 别 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.93,0:18:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我先跟你谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.47,0:18:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}坐下 听我说
