Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.47,0:19:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}老实说 如果你不娶卡拉 我可就要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.56,0:19:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我不会娶她的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.87,0:20:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 我的储物柜里就有面纱  - 我刚才那只是...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.04,0:20:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}算了吧 你们男的都是臭混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.93,0:20:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我的感觉糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.02,0:20:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我想她养这个孩子一定很需要别人的帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.86,0:20:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}是啊 她一个妇道人家很难撑下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.03,0:20:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}这会儿卡拉一定是最无依无靠的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.20,0:20:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}还有这种小黄鱼脆饼吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.49,0:20:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我们这儿没有鱼形状的脆饼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.62,0:20:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}那我刚才吃的什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.79,0:20:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}真希望我有钱 能帮她养这个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.71,0:20:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.84,0:20:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}等一下 我有个好主意 大家以前一直凑钱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.97,0:21:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}捐给少棒队 还有给孤儿送礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.85,0:21:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}这次我们要凑钱帮助卡拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.14,0:21:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我认为咱们干杯酒吧应该收养这个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.94,0:21:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}这个主意相当不赖
